      • QueryBuilder

        public QueryBuilder(ProtoMessageQueryProcessor.QueryBuilder builder)
        Constructs a QueryBuilder based on another QueryBuilder.

        All the fields of the parameter builder are copied as-is but beans, which are not set. This is done to prevent the inadvertent original builder's beans mutation. If needed, this can be accomplished explicitly via setBeans(Map) or addBean(String, Object) methods.

        Parameters:
        builder - a template QueryBuilder to copy from
